title: Alex Cooper & Hailey Bieber snack on NY bagels & play a game of Heads Up | WHO’S IN MY BATHROOM?
author: Hailey Rhode Bieber
description: We’re back in the bathroom for another very fun episode! Today I’m joined by the hilarious and lovely host of Call Her Daddy, Alex “The Father” Cooper. Watch as we reminiscence on our time living in New York (with bagels, of course), discuss female empowerment and how Call Her Daddy has evolved over the years, and play a very fun game of Heads Up!
